cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper is about learning hierarchical policies for Reinforcement Learning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The paper specifically proposes a new learning framework and model for discovering options in decision processes, which is a problem that is relevant to all of these sub-categories. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.AI, followed by cs.RO, cs.SY, and cs.NE.
